Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: Other Parents LIke Me (OPLM) is a robust online platform that supports parents who have children struggling with mental health issues, offering critical guidance and caring during a profoundly traumatic time.  At its core, OPLM is more than a website; in a very real sense, it’s like an extended family—one that features live support groups led by parents, expert speakers, a resource hub, directory and glossary. We currently have over 17 sessions each week. Our founders are passionate about this space, and their connection to OPLM is deeply personal.  They have endured life-altering challenges as parents whose children have suffered from various mental health concerns; in many cases, resources and community were unavailable or limited. These parents have enlisted a team of committed peer parents who run weekly support groups with one goal in mind: to help parents engage and move forward.  Other Parents Like Me, LLC (OPLM) lets parents know they are not alone. This online platform and virtual community is designed to create a safe space with the access and support parents need as they move from crisis to healing.  Membership includes: Daily Zoom Support Groups: Parent-led — currently offering multiple daily support groups, with early morning, identity-based, late night, and more Speakers & Expert Panels: Featuring parents and leading experts Member Accounts: Includes two unique profiles per account Parent Stories & Blog Posts: Insights into the journey of parents like you A Resource-rich Hub: Podcasts, articles, glossary, apps, books, videos, organizations  Support Directory: Professionals and organizations in the recovery/wellness space

Description: FB Displays & Designs provides event exhibits and trade show displays services.
Full Description: FB Displays & Designs, Inc. is a full-service, award-winning provider of products and services for trade shows, corporate events, retail environments and an endless array of face-to-face experiences and activations. The organization helps clients share their unique stories through a comprehensive suite of solutions that includes: exhibit design and fabrication, graphic design and production, exhibit management, digital applications, event coordination and production, strategic marketing and more. Francine Brooks, started the business in 1994 in her garage and moved it to its current location after 10 months in operation. It was then called FB Portable Displays Inc. Steady increases in sales and additional staff required regular additions to the original office/showroom. The current space now provides warehousing for clients’ display plus large showroom and offices. Their showroom, located at 338 Harris Hill, Williamsville NY, highlights a variety of displays, from table top displays to larger 20’ to 30’ configurations. Lighting, graphics, light boxes, banners, neon shelving, cabinetry, and a myriad of other display accessories, all serve in adding to that special touch. The company name was changed to FB Displays & Designs, Inc in 2005. The new name better identifies the scope of products and services the company offers. “Their main focus is to service their clients and to meet their needs. It’s important to identify what those needs are. The client’s product and services, marketing strategies, budget, trade show goals are discussed during their discovery meeting in order to design and produce a display which meets their clients’ goals.” FB Displays & Designs, Inc.’s capable and dedicated staff offers innovative designs and services that provide an informative and enjoyable experience to their clients.
